[02:29.33] A shade of sleep pass'd a veil o'er my eyes
[02:37.65] Not like them...statues of defeat...
[02:44.89] ...And I dreamt
[02:52.39] 
[03:28.61] In one room I saw a candle
[03:35.54] And in another, a votive wreath
[03:42.51] A candle to pierce the darkness
[03:50.01] And I saw an old man sitting, sitting
[03:58.07] And he was alive!